faqs.question: What is the purpose of this website?
faqs.answer: The purpose of this website is to provide a platform for developers to showcase their projects and win prizes.

faqs.question: How can I participate in the hackathon?
faqs.answer: To participate in the hackathon, you need to register on the website and submit your project before the deadline.

faqs.question: How can we help you?
faqs.answer: Unlocking possibilities for your web hosting FAQs answered. We hope you have found an answer to your question. If you need any help, please search your query on our Support Center or contact us via email.
